{"build_type":"library","description":"The single kernel-launched ROOT of the worker mechanism. Spawned by the kernel via clone (NOT fork) with a context bearing its own arena block, so render-clone endows its FS+private arena before it runs. Body is one launch_worker_binary that tail-chain-launches the boot-services collector. No self arena setup -- endow handles it.","module_name":"establish-new-mechanism-root-worker","package_name":"establish-new-mechanism-root-worker","function_definitions":{"establish-new-mechanism-root-worker":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"context","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"launch_worker_binary","target_binary":"launch-boot-services-through-as-completed-collector","cycle_type":"tail-chain"}]}}}